Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------NEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  不是這樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  但你胸部肯定變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好噁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別留下你們劣等的遺傳因子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些性慾旺盛的淫獸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  這是Bilbilder？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  女人真的都是低能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  但是很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴唇也這麼粗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你這麼說  開學習班的老頭子也是Bilbilder了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的野獸  相當的兇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也要吃醬油拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間要拌雞蛋  拌雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋要凝固了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋拌開來  拌開來  拌開來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}嗯？  拉麵？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔來啦  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}不錯啊  仁太幫我也做一份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}為什麼就給叔叔做  芽間卻沒得吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這對什麼都說可愛的習慣  可以改掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前  芽間的小書庫他也說可愛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}這不是很好嗎  對啥都能用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不用的好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放一個  別攪碎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對叔叔偏袒  偏袒  太偏袒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:01:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視電視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓貓好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸則是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡椒  胡椒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}筷子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筷子在哪  筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你怎麼了  在家裡中暑？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可愛  但很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然仁太抓的最大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個請求

Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有病  絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是積累已久的精神壓力  積累已久的精神創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏天的炎熱而產生形體…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  似乎還和青春期的性衝動相關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我精神壓力具現化的產物  存在於此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  為什麼現在才出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  還以成長後的狀態出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你問我這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  芽間應該是想實現一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼願望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連願望的內容都不知道還怎麼實現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我只是有這個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的  到底為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噴口水了  真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防護壁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}這傢伙是夏天的野獸  我的精神壓力  我的精神創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是無敵的防護壁  這下芽間無敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反防護壁的辦法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  你先回憶下自己的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  關於這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的願望是要大家一起才能實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  門鈴在響啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去又能幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之乖一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒著急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺肩膀好重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴  看不見芽間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師托我交給你的暑假作業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假？  我說你已經兩天…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宿海不一樣  我忙得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這東西隨便丟掉不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也不打算再去那垃圾學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算宿海不來  我也沒所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你這樣子很丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不拜託安鳴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「希望你和我一起實現願望  安鳴」像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先和你說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再叫她安鳴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（安鳴和肛門同音）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫就叫安城或者鳴子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴就是安鳴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對大家很好  還有很多遊戲漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經不是那時候的安鳴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去求那死三八  她也絕對不會幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死三八？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是笨女人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之她已經不是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我討厭說安鳴壞話的仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  再去一次安鳴那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拜託她吧  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去拜託一下安城  你應該也會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是安城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在和以前已經完全不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  仁太還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子加眼鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  不是要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  購物嗎  去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙齒上沾了拉麵裡的蔥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  安鳴家不在這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡以前是泡泡店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成瓦當勞了  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是芽間  還是喜歡土豆餅漢堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}那倆人以前和我一個中學的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那電影看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個電影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  會出來外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用雙截棍的阿姐在學校裡戰鬥的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也理所當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那三八給了我錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實沒人會在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城也說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不在乎我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}扯斷頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一成不變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是幻覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這果然是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於芽間的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛  很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  芽間她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…  仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  鳴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去過小仁家了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我沒敲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管這了  說正經的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便去看了下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這不關媽媽的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想讓你帶包子去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己帶去不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春期啊青春期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟人的…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑期講習班剛回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹是個升學高中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本該我也穿上的高中校服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}倒是  你怎麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集和鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  芽間她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說錯  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼芽間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在說這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中考失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進了這附近最低端的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不去學校  喊著本間芽衣子的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子不正常了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集你這傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你興奮什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一提到本間芽衣子人就會變樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點你也一樣吧  松雪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒男子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉蛋倒還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下你也明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  變化最大的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神壓力  差不多饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會想起好多好多噁心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候  那時候的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼決定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們  超和平Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Busters？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思好像就是強大的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來保護和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}哪裡的和平？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:17:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼地方  各種和平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  仁太就是隊長嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都跟在我後面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  仁太是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡芽間的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說老實話吧  超和平Busters裡不許有隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說  說  說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說呀  說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…  誰會喜歡這醜八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為她會哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為芽間是愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去下媽媽那裡  飯在微波爐裡轉一下再吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那笑容  讓我一直掛念在心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時想明天再道歉就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個明天  永遠沒有到來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  門開了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就關上唄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聰  長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢  有好多白髮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次吃咖哩都要給姐姐一份  看著好礙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  這是姐姐最喜歡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了就吃不了東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣子說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐有點呆呆的地方  可能還不知道自己已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己已經死了的事  芽間還是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  杯子自己倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  又不是我幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美地破壞了和平的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知不覺中漸漸離散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間要拌雞蛋  拌雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙會去的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要  那一天的第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要能向芽間道歉的第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了向芽間道歉而生出了芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣  就不能這麼下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的這些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太高手向了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  和正常向的差距才是浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這不是仁太嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就在這刻名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超」怎麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊寫個「走」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「走」怎麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（超和平Busters）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天  在這停止的時間又開始流動

Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間應該回到哪裡？

Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------OP------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:49.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何ページも費やして　つづられた僕らの気分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:56.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうしてか一行の　空白を埋められない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:04:05.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}押花のしおりはさんで　君と転がす使い捨ての自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:12.69,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れかけのレンガを　積み上げた場所に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:17.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}海を見渡す坂を駆けのぼって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:22.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こわいくらいに青い空と
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:30.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}右手にサイダー　左手はずっと君をさがしている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:37.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうやって今は僕の方へ　問いつめることもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:44.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ二人はすぐそこに居るのに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:50.86,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうかまた会えますように
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:05:00.69,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なんて　どうかしてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:49.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}使用好幾頁 填補了我們的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:56.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}卻彌補不了那唯一的一行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:04:05.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夾上乾花書籤 和你乘上騎一次就扔的自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:12.69,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}前往用幾乎遺忘的磚頭堆積起來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:17.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}爬上望得見海的小坡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:22.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頭上是湛藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:30.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}右手是碳酸飲料 左手一直在尋求著你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:37.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在呢 你也不會再追問我什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:44.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}兩個人明明還在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:50.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}而我卻祈願能再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:05:00.69,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可能是我的錯覺吧
